  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>POV:</strong> You're at a 2008 party and you need to use a bathroom.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You find yourself in a public restroom. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/40fb7d4c1d5e60c24f8f038133d02a13.poster.avif?t=1768716147\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/40fb7d4c1d5e60c24f8f038133d02a13.webm?t=1768716147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/40fb7d4c1d5e60c24f8f038133d02a13.mp4?t=1768716147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You explore the place and when you get inside of the empty cabin a guy next to your stall askes for some toilet paper.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/e7a55941199639470f91ba1b58d4008d.poster.avif?t=1768716147\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/e7a55941199639470f91ba1b58d4008d.webm?t=1768716147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/e7a55941199639470f91ba1b58d4008d.mp4?t=1768716147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">After giving him what he wants, he slides you a note with the message: \"STAY IN THE CABIN!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/539433712687ab452f1d59e5b5d8b17b.poster.avif?t=1768716147\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/539433712687ab452f1d59e5b5d8b17b.webm?t=1768716147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/539433712687ab452f1d59e5b5d8b17b.mp4?t=1768716147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">What you gonna do..? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you get out of the cabin, you notice that the escape door is gone... Now you have to find out if that guy trapped <strong>you</strong>, or is he trapped <strong>with you</strong>..?  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The game has:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple endings </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Strange dialogues  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Outdated memes </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In this game you can:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Make questionable choices </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solve absurd puzzles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cry </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Try to escape with your new partner or alone </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solve the mysteries of this place </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Every choice you make gets you a different outcome.</strong></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>POV:</strong> You're at a 2008 party and you need to use a bathroom.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You find yourself in a public restroom. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/40fb7d4c1d5e60c24f8f038133d02a13.poster.avif?t=1768716147\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/40fb7d4c1d5e60c24f8f038133d02a13.webm?t=1768716147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/40fb7d4c1d5e60c24f8f038133d02a13.mp4?t=1768716147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You explore the place and when you get inside of the empty cabin a guy next to your stall askes for some toilet paper.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/e7a55941199639470f91ba1b58d4008d.poster.avif?t=1768716147\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/e7a55941199639470f91ba1b58d4008d.webm?t=1768716147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/e7a55941199639470f91ba1b58d4008d.mp4?t=1768716147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">After giving him what he wants, he slides you a note with the message: \"STAY IN THE CABIN!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/539433712687ab452f1d59e5b5d8b17b.poster.avif?t=1768716147\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/539433712687ab452f1d59e5b5d8b17b.webm?t=1768716147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946550/extras/539433712687ab452f1d59e5b5d8b17b.mp4?t=1768716147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">What you gonna do..? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you get out of the cabin, you notice that the escape door is gone... Now you have to find out if that guy trapped <strong>you</strong>, or is he trapped <strong>with you</strong>..?  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The game has:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple endings </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Strange dialogues  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Outdated memes </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In this game you can:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Make questionable choices </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solve absurd puzzles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cry </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Try to escape with your new partner or alone </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solve the mysteries of this place </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Every choice you make gets you a different outcome.</strong></h2>",
